{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662920/extras/the_lawless_frontier.png?t=1536964287\" /><br>Running your new gang will be a daunting task. Facing the lethal outcomes will be a harsh reality. Decisive tactics will be the difference between success and failure.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/662920/extras/about_game_header.png?t=1536964287\" /><br><strong>WESTSLINGERS</strong><br>is a single-player western real-time tactics game where you form your own gang to take on distinct missions in the bleak settlements of the wild west. You select up to a team of four to ride into each town to execute a series of objectives. Assemble the best crew of outlaws and direct them with devious tactics to attempt the most challenging of scenarios.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Recruit a band of outlaws and develop them into an elite gang.<br></li><li>Freeze time in tactics mode to analyze the situation and form a plan.<br></li><li>Flaunt mastery of line-of-sight and timing in a showcase of tactics.<br></li><li>Secure buildings to gain bonuses that ensure mission success.<br></li><li>Create your own solutions to 24 objective-based missions.<br></li><li>Challenge your previous bests to earn medals and experience.<br></li><li>Leverage the hard-earned talents of each gang member.<br></li><li>Engage non-scripted and responsive AI in combat and deception.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Notorious","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/662920/6066a509669c1b72209f81bdf18553615f3f0946.jpg"},{"name":"Down in History","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/662920/c9af409113de9cabbd526c6caaf2fa4c83d5b2c1.jpg"},{"name":"Escape Artist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/662920/4980e5672637d199f5767dabe3c87480d01